snippet.title: Pax Dei | Early Access Announcement
snippet.description:
Pax Dei Early Access is on prepurchase on our website: https://PlayPaxDei.com/early-access

Pax Dei is a social sandbox MMO under development and inspired by the legends of medieval Europe. Discover a world where myths are real, ghosts exist, and magic is an everyday part of life. Join thousands of players as you explore the land, build your home, forge your reputation, and shape your own stories. What world will you make?

We’re hard at work developing Pax Dei, and we can’t wait to share it with you! Stay up-to-date on our progress, upcoming playtests, and more:

❖ Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1995520/Pax_Dei/
❖ Join the community on Discord: https://discord.gg/paxdei
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#playPaxDei

You can also find us on...
❖ Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayPaxDei
❖ Instagram: https://instagram.com/playpaxdei/
